8.10 ARIMA vs ETS

fets <- function(x, h) {
  forecast(ets(x), h = h)
}

farima <- function(x, h) {
  forecast(auto.arima(x), h = h)
}
air <- window(ausair, start=1990)
e1 <- tsCV(air, fets, h = 1)
e2 <- tsCV(air, farima, h = 1)
mean(e1^2, na.rm = TRUE)
[1] 7.864374
mean(e2^2, na.rm = TRUE)
[1] 9.622164
air |>
  ets() |>
  forecast() |>
  autoplot()


air |>
  auto.arima() |>
  forecast() |>
  autoplot()

cement <- window(qcement, start = 1988)
cement |>
  autoplot()
